        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Senior Legal Hotline Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill permits the Administration on Aging to award competitive grants to certain nonprofit organizations or partnerships to establish or maintain statewide senior legal hotlines to provide free services to older individuals.</p>]]>
